    <character-template name="Body Guard" points="10">
        <description>
            <background>
                <para>
                    Body guards are generally hired by rich merchants
                    who want a bit of hired muscle to protect them.
                    They  do  however  want  that  muscle  to  look
                    presentable, and have the sense to keep alert and do
                    their job well. Because a shield is often too bulky to
                    carry around in polite company, body guards tend to
                    favour the short sword and dagger.
                </para>

                <para>
                    Because a body guard is rarely a noble, they are not
                    permitted to carry noble weapons.
                </para>
            </background>
        </description>
        
