    <character-template name="Mercenary" points="8">
        <description>
            <background>
                <para>
                    Mercenaries are found all across Harn, taking pay
                    in return for fighting other people's wars. Most of
                    their life is spent sitting around waiting for
                    something to happen. Occasionally they fight, and
                    often they die.
                </para>
                <para>
                    Some mercenaries will be landless nobles, though they
                    are rare. Most nobles who take up fighting for others
                    do not consider themselves mercenaries, since they are
                    fighting for a cause, not money. The food, lodgings
                    and 'upkeep' which is paid to them is very different
                    to the coin (plus meals and a bed) which is paid to
                    mercenaries.
                </para>
            </background>
        </description>

