    <character-template name="Gozyda Warrior">
        <description>
            <background>
                <para>
                The Gozyda are forest tribesmen who inhabit hte Mimea Hills
                between Kanday and Tharda. They are loosely allied with the
                former against the latter, subsisting on hunting and raiding.
                They welcome many bandits and outlaws into their ranks.
                </para>
                <para>
                Gozyda warriors are fond of guerrilla tactics against their
                enemies, and are skilled woodsmen. Unlike some other tribes
                in Harn, the Gozyda are not afraid of making use of new
                technology for themselves, and are willing to trade and raid
                for quality swords and armour where necessary.
                </para>
                <para>
